OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and windy with rain
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, heavy at times.
OL,7,FBecoming dry but still cloudy in the
OL,8,Fearly afternoon, before bright spells
OL,9,Fdevelop later, though the odd shower
OL,10,Fpossible around the north coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay mostly dry with
OL,13,Fclear spells through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight, but the odd shower possible
OL,15,Faround the north coast. Breezy at
OL,16,Ftimes in the evening, easing overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
