OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLargely dry with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells, but chance of the odd
OL,7,Fshower. A bit cooler than recent days.
OL,8,FChance of rain in the southeast in the
OL,9,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FChance
OL,12,Fof cloud and rain in southeast at
OL,13,Ffirst Saturday, otherwise dry and
OL,14,Fbright. Cloudy and windy at times with
OL,15,Foccasional spells of rain on Sunday
OL,16,Fand Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
